      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·鄭風·002.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">將仲子.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>將仲子兮，無踰我里，無折我樹杞。豈敢愛之？畏我父母。仲可懷也，父母之言，亦可畏也。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>I pray you, Mr. Chung,
Do not come leaping into my hamlet;
Do not break my willow trees.
Do I care for them?
But I fear my parents.
You, O Chung, are to be loved,
But the words of my parents
Are also to be feared.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__guofeng-zhengfeng-002__002__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sheking-1871-ocr">
