      <prop type="x-translation-ref">將仲子.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>將仲子兮，無踰我園，無折我樹檀。豈敢愛之？畏人之多言。仲可懷也，人之多言，亦可畏也。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>I pray you, Mr. Chung,
Do not come leaping into my garden;
Do not break my sandal trees.
Do I care for them?
But I dread the talk of people.
You, O Chung, are to be loved,
But the talk of people
Is also to be feared.</seg>
      </tuv>
